{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 180°C.  Grease a deep-sided casserole dish (approx. 20 cm) and set aside.","Place lemon peel and sugar into mixing bowl and mill <nobr>20 sec\/speed 9<\/nobr>.","Add butter and mix <nobr>20 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Beat <nobr>10-20 sec\/speed 3<\/nobr>, until well combined. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Mix <nobr>30 sec\/speed 3<\/nobr>, slowly adding 1 egg yolk at a time through hole in mixing bowl lid. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>.","Add flour, lemon juice and milk and combine <nobr>10 sec\/speed 2<\/nobr>.","Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and combine <nobr>5 sec\/speed 2<\/nobr>. Pour mixture into prepared casserole dish.","Thoroughly wash and dry mixing bowl and butterfly whisk. <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Place egg whites into mixing bowl and whisk <nobr>2-3 min\/speed 4<\/nobr>, <strong>without measuring cup<\/strong>, until soft peaks form. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>.","Gently fold egg whites through lemon mixture. Place casserole dish into a large baking dish and fill up baking dish halfway with boiling water. Bake for 40-45 minutes (180°C), until golden. Dust with icing sugar and serve while warm with cream (optional)."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["125 g unsalted butter, plus extra for greasing","1 lemon, zest only, no white pith","220 g raw sugar","4 eggs, separated","75 g plain flour","80 g freshly squeezed lemon juice (see Tip)","310 g milk","boiling water","icing sugar, for dusting","thickened cream, to serve (optional)"]}],"id":"r223131","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-mqYY7sDaX8o\/XZWd4CLQUlI\/AAAAAAAAerY\/4ok-j2j7ywIiJgxsPEmwZcNLadFc0x17wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Nwq6kloUa1YRuPzr.png","title":"Lemon delicious","publishedAt":"2018-07-30T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"6.5 g","fat":"25.2 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"40 g","calories":"17